'''安格斯·特纳·琼斯'''（{{lang-en|Angus Turner Jones}}，{{bd|1993年|10月8日|||catIdx=J}}），[[美国|美国]]演员。他因出演[[哥伦比亚广播公司|哥伦比亚广播公司]]电视剧[[好汉两个半|好汉两个半]]（2003年–2015年）中的杰克·哈珀而成名。

==生涯==
除了《好汉两个半》，琼斯还参演过《[[警犬追杀令|警犬追杀令]]》、《[[新手上路_(2002年电影)|新手上路]]》、《[[爱到房倒屋塌_(电影)|爱到房倒屋塌]]》、《[[森林泰山2|森林泰山2]]》和《[[圣诞祝福|圣诞祝福]]》。

琼斯在两季（26集）结束后签下了790万美元的合同和外加500,000美元的奖金。这意味着他出演《好汉两个半》每集片酬约300,000美元，使他成为片酬最高的童星。<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.tmz.com/2010/10/07/two-and-a-half-men-angus-t-jones-contract-charlie-sheen-rich-300000-jake-harper/ | work=TMZ | title=Two and a Half Men' Kid Scores MASSIVE Contract | first=TMZ | last=Staff | date=October 8, 2010 | accessdate=February 21, 2011 | archive-date=2021-01-26 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126024328/https://www.tmz.com/2010/10/07/two-and-a-half-men-angus-t-jones-contract-charlie-sheen-rich-300000-jake-harper/ | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/two-and-half-men-kid-28937 | work=Associated Press | publisher=The Hollywood Reporter | title=Two and a Half Men' kid signs $300K-ep deal - Makes him highest-paid child TV star | first=Lindsay | last=Powers | date=October 8, 2010 | accessdate=February 21, 2011 | archive-date=2019-12-06 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191206205648/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/two-and-half-men-kid-28937 | dead-url=no }}</ref>

==著名事件==
2008年6月7日，琼斯联合[[达科他·范宁|达科他·范宁]]、[[小库珀·古丁|小库珀·古丁]]、[[范·基默|范·基默]]等明星以及曾经在《爱到房倒屋塌》中合作过的明星[[金柏莉·布朗|金柏莉·布朗]]给予第一个帮助虐童的明星组织支持。<ref>[http://www.theinsider.com/news/957001_New_Wave_of_Celebrity_Kids_Making_A_Difference_First_Star_Come_Be_A_Kid_Again  New Wave of Celebrity Kids Making A Difference: First Star "Come Be A Kid Again!"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.theinsider.com/news/957001_New_Wave_of_Celebrity_Kids_Making_A_Difference_First_Star_Come_Be_A_Kid_Again |date=20090130020435 }} The Insider. 2008. Retrieved on 2009-06-15.</ref>

2008年8月26日，琼斯与[[玛德琳·奇玛|玛德琳·奇玛]]、[[汤姆·巴里|汤姆·巴里]]和[[布兰登·巴拉什|布兰登·巴拉什]]参加一年一度的“摇滚乐梦幻营（Rock 'N Roll Fantasy Camp）”。<ref>[http://www.nypost.com/seven/06062008/tv/starr_report_114134.htm  Rock 'N Roll Fantasy Camp] STARR REPORT - New York Post, June 6, 2008. Retrieved on 2009-06-14.</ref>

2008年10月4日，琼斯与[[米兰达·科斯格罗夫|米兰达·科斯格罗夫]]、[[梅甘·杰特·马丁|梅甘·杰特·马丁]]、[[雷·李欧塔|雷·李欧塔]]、[[赛琳娜·戈麦斯|赛琳娜·戈麦斯]]和[[Shailene_Woodley|Shailene Woodley]]参加[[田纳西州|田纳西州]][[孟菲斯_(田纳西州)|孟菲斯]]圣犹达儿童研究医院组织的Variety's Power of Youth benefit活动。<ref>[http://www.stjude.org/stjude/v/index.jsp?vgnextoid=c92a0257c3a7b110VgnVCM1000001e0215acRCRD&vgnextchannel=9777dcb97214e110VgnVCM1000001e0215acRCRD  Variety and Target announce the 2008 Target Presents Variety's Power of Youth to benefit St. Jude] {{Wayback|url=http://www.stjude.org/stjude/v/index.jsp?vgnextoid=c92a0257c3a7b110VgnVCM1000001e0215acRCRD&vgnextchannel=9777dcb97214e110VgnVCM1000001e0215acRCRD |date=20110613020025 }} St. Jude Children's Research Hospital. July 31, 2008. Retrieved on 2009-06-14.</ref>

2009年10月，一起出演《好汉两个半》的演员[[乔恩·克莱尔|乔恩·克莱尔]]在“大哥大姐新星晚会上”授予琼斯“2009年新星”奖。<ref>[http://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/big-brothers-big-sisters-of-los-angeles-announce-honorees-for-2009-rising-stars-gala-65587967.html  Big Brothers Big Sisters of Los Angeles] {{Wayback|url=http://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/big-brothers-big-sisters-of-los-angeles-announce-honorees-for-2009-rising-stars-gala-65587967.html |date=20121015171700 }} PRNewswire.com. October 22, 2009. Retrieved on 2009-10-30.</ref>

